"]}],"
",["$r","p",null,{"children":["If you use CSS-in-JS, we recommend a combination of the first two approaches (CSS files for static styles, inline styles for dynamic styles). ",["$r","strong",null,{"children":["We don’t recommend runtime ",["$r","code",null,{"children":"<style>"}]," tag injection for two reasons:"]}]]}],"
